channel.title: Elemental Universe (A server you won't forget)
channel.description:
[ul][size=20pt][CENTER] [size=50pt]Elemental Universe[/size] [size=30pt]A server that will actually happen.[/size]
[B]Information.[/B] Well, i have been working alone on this server for a while. The base is devo 2.7. BUT you wouldn't know it because i have changed nearly everything from combat to networking and loggin. I thought it was time to release a project thread as it is near completion and has features left to do only. [color=blue] [I][U]Server Information[/U][/I] [list] [*]Server Combat Experience is 90x runescapes. [*]Server Skill Experience is 40x Runescapes [*]Client is a custom client, with all 474 emotes. [*]Money Making is a challenge, as it increases economy. [*]No Pvp Items. Or Total Recoloured items.(pvp might change) [*]Extremely stable server, holds 100 on 512mb. [*]Bosses Have Realistic Runescape Feel, near exact attacks. [*]AND MORE! [/list]
[color=purple][size=10pt][I][U]Minigames[/U][/I] [list] [*]100% Runescape Barrows. [*]Pest Control Minigame, Based on Killing. [*]10 Waves of FightCave - Realistic Experience, [*]FightPits. [*]Duel Arena. [*]Mage Arena. [*]Magic Training Area. [/list]
[color=teal] [U]Bosses[/U] [list] [*]Dagannoth Kings - Very dangerous, Bring a team. [*]Kbd - 3 Fire attacks, 1 Melee attack. [*]Chaos Elemental - 3 magic attacks, 1 range attack, 1 melee attack. [*]General Graadar - Range + Melee attack, With followers with there own combat style. [*]Kree'Arra - ^Same as above, but 1 melee and 2 range attacks. [*]Commander Zylan - ^Same but a melee, and magic attack. [*]Kalphite Queen - Melee, range and magic attack. [*]Tormented Demon's - Fully animated, all 3 attacks with shield. (NO PRAYER) [/list]
[size=10pt] [U]Quests[/U] [LIST=1] [*]Drogo's Helper - Supply of Pickaxes. [*]Magick's Secrets - Ancient magic. [*]Unethicle God's - Tormented Demons [*]Magick's Secrets p2 - Lunar Magic. [*]MAYBE MORE![/ul] [/size]
[color=limegreen][size=10pt]LATEST UPDATES.[/size][code] New networking, and login. Complete syi protection Completely new packet system. Fully Functioning report system. Got a client developer because i can't do both and make deadline. Full Godwars Map + Ancient Cavern. More Flexible npc combat. Process to events conversion More lunar spells Perfecting Door system All Process converted to events Memory issues fixed. Full Potion system with level returning/rising. Took time to check all skills to make sure they are efficient and work correctly. Full Npc Transformation mask (thanks blake). Moving all files to my new Desktop computer, 4 core, 8gb, i5 processer FIXING ALL THE SKILLS TO WORK PERFECT. Fixed alot of issues causing server to lag [/CODE][/CENTER]
[B][I][U][CENTER]Media - More to come! [IMG]http://i462.photobucket.com/albums/qq345/theinjuredonee/gwd.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i462.photobucket.com/albums/qq345/theinjuredonee/Lootshare.png[/img] [url=http://www.youtube.com/ElementalUniverse]http://www.youtube.com/ElementalUniverse[/url][/CENTER]
[left][b][i][u]Snippets. Code i write while coding the server.[/u][/i][/b] Wyvern - Delta (for friend): http://pastebin.com/f3c726c14 Gem Crafting - All: http://pastebin.com/f42457462[/left] Woodcutting Base: http://pastebin.com/f279cf28c Mining Base: http://pastebin.com/f6a65acd1
[I]Credits[/I] Everyone =p
[U][color=purple][I][B][U]Release Date: January[/U][/B][/I][/U]
